Working in the beauty field was a dream to her . The purpose to reach and serve others . The satisfaction , thrill she’d get from content individual/ clients pushed her  forward.

2012 focusing mainly as a makeup artist for the luxurious brand we all familiar with Christian Dior.  Debating A lifetime opportunity when offered international trainer's position for the company &  her mother's proposition to join her at her newly aesthetic / beauty salon. The hardest settlement . Choosing family over her so called "dream job" which quickly became her dream career.

Following her mother's footsteps to become a hairdresser, aesthetician & PMU artist, to complete her knowledge in the industry. They rapidly became one of the most successful & busiest beauty salon in the south shore of Montreal. Building today, over 17 years of rewarding career in the beauty industry.

Today Hazia Payman is a devoted mother to two beautiful boys. She not only contribute talents towards her clients & students, but also, inspire individuals who seek to become professionals . As she was thought well from her own mother… she will teach you craft , passion and experience gained  throughout these years & the knowledge through mistakes she today  polished . Teaching  to who would want to learn more than just basic skills.  With more than 50,000 procedures to her name, from hair, makeup, PMU, aesthetics and much more… She continues to invest all effort into fully satisfying clients / and students . Hazia nurture her dream " team member"  hoping to maintain the quality of an exceptional service and customer satisfaction.

Know your worth. Invest time & money on yourself 📖 🧠 🏃🏻‍♀️… explore yourself & most importantly LOVE YOURSELF . Life is a beautiful journey with full of surprises.. everyday is a new beginning & a new chance to get to explore yourself even more.
